    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n今、テレビをつけたら、瑠依ちゃん達が！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nI just turned on the TV‚ and Rui-chan and the others are on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1335569245474684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLE、電撃移籍記者会見……\nそんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE’s Shocking Transfer Press Conference…\nI can’t believe it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.788076887375269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "これ、生放送？\n随分と慌ただしいわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this a live broadcast?\nIt looks awfully hectic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "会場の押さえと、マスコミへの連絡の期間を考えれば\n元々、姫野さんは準備をしていたってことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you consider the time it takes to rent a space and contact the media‚\nit’s clear Himeno-san had all of this set up for quite a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "どうして……\n私達、これからみんなで頑張るって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?…\nWe promised we’d push through together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にライブもやろうって、楽しみにしてたのに……！\nどうして！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were all so excited about doing a joint concert together!\nWhy?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "しっ、瑠依が話すわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shh! Rui’s about to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.09435364405314,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4500.000000000056,
          "startTime": 40.5943536440532
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6072.313022613521,
          "startTime": 42.166666666666664
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4905.646355946857,
          "startTime": 41
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6405.646355946857,
          "startTime": 42.5
        },
        {
