    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 39.56102031071981
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 39.56102031071981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-reporter001.m4a",
      "text": "今回の電撃移籍の経緯を教えていただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you tell us what caused this shocking transfer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.59435364405315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 44.49435354868575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテはみなさんも知っての通り\n業界有数の芸能事務所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pret-A-Porter is‚ as you all know‚\nan industry-leading talent agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.027686882019054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私達がより飛躍するためには移籍した方がいい\nと考えました。あくまでも合理的な判断です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We thought it best to switch agencies if we really wanted\nan opportunity to shine. It was simply the most logical decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.09403597513835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 57.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-reporter002.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロから星見プロに移籍して\nまだ日も浅かったと思うのですが？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it was only just recently that you transferred\nfrom Van Productions to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 62.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロとは契約上、在籍日数の縛りはありませんから\n何も問題はないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our contract with Hoshimi Productions didn’t bind us with an enrollment period‚\nso there are no issues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 69.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バンプロの社長が、つい先日逮捕されましたが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The president of Van Productions was just arrested a little while ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その件についてどう思われますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are your thoughts on that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 75.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "つ、罪を犯したのなら\n社会的責任を取るべき、だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-if he’s guilty of a crime‚\nthen I think he should repay his debt to society.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2866.66666666666,
          "startTime": 78.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3333333333258,
          "startTime": 78.36666666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.6666666666656,
          "startTime": 79
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.666666666666,
          "startTime": 79.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 81.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達には直接関係のない話、ですので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that matter has nothing to do with us‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 87.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バンプロに対しても星見プロに対しても、随分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem awfully “cool-headed‚” one might even say‚ heartless‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "クールというか、ドライな対応に見えるのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in your response to both Van Productions and Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私達の言動をどうとらえるかは、みなさん次第です\nどう解釈していただいても構いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How you perceive our words is up to you.\nWe don’t care how you interpret them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.333333333338,
          "startTime": 98.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.3333333333285,
          "startTime": 99.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.333333333334,
          "startTime": 99.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 100.26666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6299.999999999997,
          "startTime": 100.76666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6766.666666666666,
          "startTime": 101.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 102.4
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.66666666666669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……おかしい\n瑠依さん達はこんな冷たい言い方をする人じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something’s off…\nRui and her girls would never say such heartless things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、まるでわざと印象を悪くするような話し方ね\n彼女ならもっとうまい振る舞いが出来るはず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. It’s almost like they’re purposely trying to tarnish their own image.\nI know she could have handled this with more tact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さん、これはどういうことなんですか？\nどうしてトリエルが移籍会見なんてしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno-san‚ what is the meaning of this?\nWhy is TRINITYAiLE doing a press conference over their transfer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだ彼女達と正式な契約は結べていないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We still haven’t signed a formal contract with them yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、先に既成事実を作らせてもらったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I had them create a fait accompli in advance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
